{
  "stem": "13258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the first military Soviet one we saw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we went back into Tarnopol, and were first housed by some Jews who had-- there were immediately lots of organizations who were trying to help.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The first couple of nights, we slept in an abandoned apartment on straw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But then we found some people, and some people were sending us to other people, and we were housed here and there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And suddenly we met more people from our city.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went back to the brewery and found out that my girlfriend had arrived there with her parents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were, had been running away from the farm, too, but they had horses, so they went with the horses with the wagon.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I got a job in the brewery schlepping sacks with barley and, and, and, and malt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My father subsequently got a job with the shoemakers as an accountant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then we rented a room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But in the meantime, one more thing happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "One day, a lot of men from Katowice arrived.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They explained to us that they had gotten a summons from the Nazis to appear on a certain day at the sports palace in the city and had been given a list what to bring with them-- and there were how many pairs of underwear, socks, so on, so on, an ax if they have one, a spade, tools, anything, because they are going to be sent to work somewhere.",
      "word_count": 70
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "What they did, they drove them to a station called-- a rail station called [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's not far from where our train abandoned us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were told, get out, and they were pointed in that direction.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
